channel.description:
Firstly download this files [b]Client.jar[/b] [url=http://fubergen.gethost.nl/client.jar]fubergen.gethost.nl/client.jar[/url] 2. open notepad, copy this and paste to notepad
My Applet Page Java is not installed on your machine or your browser does not allowed Java Applet to run

Get the latest Java technology at http://www.java.com/
save file as client.html upload to your webhost as freewebs. [b]DEMO[/b] [url=http://fubergen.gethost.nl/client.html]fubergen.gethost.nl/client.html[/url] webclient is based off v7.1 Thanks goes for Fubergen, im just posting this if someone thinks, why im posting, i got permission from roju
